==English==
{{wikipedia}}
[[Image:Bufo bufo couple during migration(2005).jpg|thumb|right|Two common toads (''Bufo bufo'' ssp. ''spinosus'')]]
===Etymology===
Old English ''[[tada|tāda]]'', a shortening of ''[[tadige|tādiġe]]'', of unknown origin.

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/təʊd/}}
*{{audio|en-us-toad.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-əʊd|-əʊd]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# An [[amphibian]] similar to a [[frog]] with bigger back legs and more [[ragged]] skin.
# A very unpleasant man.

